INSERT INTO `Operative` VALUES ('AEL','BOK','BOK',3,'DAW','Dire Avenger Warrior','These operatgives are famed for being as deadly on the attack as they are immovable in the defence, and are regarded as being the most tactically flexible of all the Aspects. They use their shuriken catapults to create an impenetrable storm of monomolecular blades.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','4+','8','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, DIRE AVENGER, WARRIOR',0,''),('AEL','BOK','BOK',0,'DAX','Dire Avenger Exarch','These warriors are masters of their Aspect and devoted to their craftworld. In keeping with the tactical felxibility of their Aspect, all are master marksmen and bladesmen, as at ease shredding foes with volleys of razor-sharp shuriken as they are duelling enemy heroes in single combat.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','3+','9','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, LEADER, DIRE AVENGER, EXARCH',0,''),('AEL','BOK','BOK',4,'HBW','Howling Banshee Warrior','The piercing, psychosonic scream that precedes the assault of these bone-armoured operatives renders those who hear it all but helpless. These shock waves buy the Howling Banshees time enough to strike, each one taking a head with a sweep of their glittering power weapon.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','4+','8','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, HOWLING BANSHEE, WARRIOR',0,''),('AEL','BOK','BOK',1,'HBX','Howling Banshee Exarch','Not only do the skills in elegant swordplay displayed by a Hownling Banshee Exarch exceed those of the warriors she leads, but so harrowing and biting are her cries that their echoing reverberations haunt those who hear them long after their screams have died away.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','3+','9','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, LEADER, HOWLING BANSHEE, EXARCH',0,''),('AEL','BOK','BOK',5,'SSW','Striking Scorpion Warrior','With limitless patience, after stalking their prey for hours or waiting in position for days, Striking Scorpions burst from concealment. With chainswords whirring and mandiblasters spitting needles of white fire, the Aspect Warriors\' emerald green armour is soon streaked red.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','4+','8','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, STRIKING SCORPION, WARRIOR',0,''),('AEL','BOK','BOK',2,'SSX','Striking Scorpion Exarch','These sinister figures are even more skilled than the Aspect Warriors they lead. With the gigantic chainsword known as the Biting Blade, a Striking Scorpion Exarch can cleave their foes in two with a single swing, and use their scorpion\'s claw to tear open Space Marin power armour with ease.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','3+','9','BLADES OF KHAINE, ALEDARI, ASURYANI, LEADER, STRIKING SCORPION, EXARCH',0,''),('AEL','COM','KBL',0,'GNR','Kabalite Gunner','Drukhari weapons technology is far in advance of the Imperium\'s. Blasters utilise darklight, a mysterious substance that vaporises armour. Shredders, meanwhile, unleash an expanding mesh of barbed monofilaments that entangle the victim in an invisible, slicing net.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <KABAL>, KABALITE, GUNNER',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('AEL','COM','KBL',0,'HGNR','Kabalite Heavy Gunner','The Drukhari go to battle with powerful weapons for dealing with hordes of opposing troops, battle tanks, and heavily armoured warriors. Kabalites wield Splinter Cannons or Dark Lances to deal with these threats, and when battle is done their kill tallies are jaw-dropping.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <KABAL>, KABALITE, HEAVY GUNNER',0,'Marksman'),('AEL','COM','KBL',0,'SYB','Sybarite','To lead formations of such cruel creatures as Kabalite Warriors requires beings of exceptional ruthlessness and murderous fighting skill. Sybarites have demonstrated their deep sadism on dozens of raids, and rule through fear as much as their effective combat skills.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <KABAL>, KABALITE, LEADER, SYBARITE',0,'Combat,Marksman,Scout'),('AEL','COM','KBL',0,'WAR','Kabalite Warrior','Kabalite Warriors conduct murderous raids cald in blade-edged, segmented armour. Highly skilled fighters who eschew such notions as honour, they unleash flurries of toxin-coated shards from their Splinter weapons whose poinsonous effects are swift to kill','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <KABAL>, KABALITE, WARRIOR',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('AEL','COM','WYCH',0,'FTR','Wych Fighter','Many Wyches take to the field bearing wicked gladiatorial weapons. Some ensnare foes in the hooked mesh of shardnets before impaling them with twin-bladed spears. Others lash enemies with flicks of their Razorflails or shred them with the crystalline blades of their Hydra Gauntlets.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','6+','8','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <WYCH CULT>, WYCH, FIGHTER',0,'Combat,Scout'),('AEL','COM','WYCH',0,'HEK','Hekatrix','Hekatarii lead Wyches on realspace raids and in the arenas. Countless are the enemies they have slain, and many have achieved a degree of fame in Commorragh only to hunger for more. Cruel and merciless, they lead their charges ruthlessly and lust after their foes\' suffering.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','6+','9','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <WYCH CULT>, LEADER, WYCH, HEKATRIX',0,'Combat,Scout'),('AEL','COM','WYCH',0,'WAR','Wych Warrior','Wyches are acrobatic murder-artists who take great delight in displaying their formidable blade skills. They twist and dart around their foes\' attacks in combat, making the most talented warriors appear clumsy in comparison.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','6+','8','COMMORRITE, AELDARI, DRUKHARI, <WYCH CULT>, WYCH, WARRIOR',0,'Combat,Scout'),('AEL','COR','COR',0,'FA','Voidscarred Felarch','Felarchs are veteran Corsairs, with centuries or even millenia of experience reaving the starts. They have fought countless different races and mastered numerous weapons, making them deadly enemies for any who face them.',