he Ruinous Powers of Chaos.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','6+','12','ASSASSIN EXECUTION FORCE, IMPERIUM, VINDICARE ASSASSIN',2,'Marksman,Scout'),('HBR','SHV','SHV',2,'FTR','Space Hulk Veteran Fighter','Always seen at the spearhead of any Astartes assault, Terminators will use close combat weapons such as the Thunder Hammer and Lightning Claws to crush their enemies in ruthless assaults.\nWith these brutally efficient weapons, combined with their battlefield experience and immense bulk, they make short work of the enemies of Mankind.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','2+','18','SPACE MARINE, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ASTARTES, TERMINATOR, SPACE HULK VETERAN, FIGHTER',0,''),('HBR','SHV','SHV',1,'GNR','Space Hulk Veteran Gunner','Terminator Gunners provide devastating and accurate fire for their brothers.\nArmed with either an Assault Cannon to unleash hails of long range firepower at the enemy, or Heavy Flamers to cover entrenched enemies in torrents of flame.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','2+','18','SPACE MARINE, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ASTARTES, TERMINATOR, SPACE HULK VETERAN, GUNNER',0,''),('HBR','SHV','SHV',0,'SGT','Space Hulk Veteran Sergeant','Each Terminator is a Veteran and competent battlefield leader in their own right.\nThose who prove their leadership will be promoted to Sergeant and be tasked with leading squads of Terminators into battle.\nThese level-header and brave Veterans are capable of achieving the most difficult of missions almost singlehandedly.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','2+','18','SPACE MARINE, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ASTARTES, TERMINATOR, SPACE HULK SERGEANT, LEADER',0,''),('HBR','SHV','SHV',3,'WAR','Space Hulk Veteran Warrior','Only the greatest heroes of Mankind are permitted to wear Terminator armour.\nCenturies of battlefield experience combined with some of the Imperium\'s most devastating weaponry make these Veterans the perfect battlefield asset to achieve a number of missions, from boarding newly discovered Space Hulks to assaulting enemy Titans.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','3','1','3','2+','18','SPACE MARINE, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ASTARTES, TERMINATOR, SPACE HULK VETERAN, WARRIOR',0,''),('HBR','WDR','WDR',3,'WDB','Warpdiver Breacher','Breachers sacrifice their mobility to be able to bear the mightiest warpdiver weapons and to unleash volley after volley of heavy fire; because nothing protects imperial space better than bullets.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','WARPDIVERS, IMPERIUM, ASTRA MILITARUM, WARPDIVER, BREACHER',2,''),('HBR','WDR','WDR',4,'WDM','Warpdiver Marksman','Marksmen prefer to take down their foes from afar, putting them down with powerful ammunitions and precise shots before they become a threat to other warpdivers.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','WARPDIVERS, IMPERIUM, ASTRA MILITARUM, WARPDIVER, MARKSMAN',2,''),('HBR','WDR','WDR',5,'WDS','Warpdiver Specialist','Armed with some of the most advanced equipment available to the Astra Militarum, warpdiver specialists are deployed to take care of xenos and heretics with tailored weaponry.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','WARPDIVERS, IMPERIUM, ASTRA MILITARUM, WARPDIVER, SPECIALIST',2,''),('HBR','WDR','WDR',2,'WDT','Warpdiver Trooper','Fresh out of training and armed with standard-issue rifles and righteous hate for xenos, troopers constitute the backbone of any warpdiver team.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','2','3','4+','8','WARPDIVERS, IMPERIUM, ASTRA MILITARUM, WARPDIVER, TROOPER',2,''),('HBR','WDR','WDR',1,'WDV','Warpdiver Veteran','Warpdivers that successfully return from their first dives are destined to become veterans, unflinching paragons of liberty ready to the deliver the wrath of the Emperor in brutal close quarter combat','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','WARPDIVERS, IMPERIUM, ASTRA MILITARUM, WARPDIVER, LEADER, VETERAN',2,''),('IMP','AES','AES',1,'CAST','Arbites Castigator','It is the Castigator\'s role to ensure that the guilty receive due punishment, their hood-like helps steeling their resolve against curses and pleas alike. Once the quarry is located, the Castigator is charged with their subdual by any means - a task they perform with zealous dedication.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, CASTIGATOR',0,'Combat,Staunch'),('IMP','AES','AES',2,'CHI','Arbites Chirurgant','These Arbitrators are highly skilled medical specialists, used to treating debilitating wounds inflicted by those resisting detention. They are also skilled in the tactical questioning of prisoners and have studied the limits to which the body can be pushed to elicit answers.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, MEDIC, ARBITES, CHIRURGANT',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('IMP','AES','AES',3,'GNR','Arbites Gunner','Gunners provide substantial firepower to Exaction Squad operations using weapons such as Heavy Stubbers - rapid-firing cannons whose solid shot can scythe through mobs. More specialist weapons may fire chemicals that paralyze, or grenades that crack open doors and armour alike.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, GUNNER',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('IMP','AES','AES',4,'LSH','Arbites Leashmaster','Leashmasters are specialists who command the caniform servitors known as Cyber-Mastiffs. They direct override the construct\'s basic protocols with advanced commands, and broadcast shouted orders to their guilt-ridden prey via the Cyber-Mastiff\'s emitters.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, LEASHMASTER',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('IMP','AES','AES',6,'MAL','Arbites Malocator','Technically gifted, Malocators carry bio-sample extractors to gather trace evidence on their team\'s quarry. They operate with an icy calm under fire, scrutinising evidence via their veriscant multi-lens array and informing their team of enemy weaknesses.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, MALOCATOR',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('IMP','AES','AES',7,'MRK','Arbites Marksman','The rabble-rouser lurking behind those they incite, the heavily armed bodyguard, or the fleeing criminal about to escape - such are the targets of the Marksman. Their long-barrelled shotguns fire shells so powerful that they leave wounds more akin to gory craters than bullet holes.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, MARKSMAN',0,'Marksman'),('IMP','AES','AES',0,'PE','Arbites Proctor-Exactant','Exaction Squads are selected and let by Proctor-Exactants. These experienced Arbitrators are ruthless tacticians and savvy fighters. They are also intimidating embodiments of Imperial justice and employ nuncio-aquilas to broadcast deafening orations that cow the guilty into submission.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, LEADER, ARBITES, PROCTOR-EXACTANT',0,'Combat,Staunch,Marksman'),('IMP','AES','AES',8,'REV','Arbites Revelatum','Revelatums reconnoitre their target\'s movements in advance of the rest of the team, scouting hideouts and ascertaining criminal contacts. They then lead other Arbitrators straight to the guilty, using their soulguilt scanners to identify threats to their fellow officers.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, REVELATUM',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('IMP','AES','AES',5,'RVR','R-VR Cyber-Mastiff','Arbitrators employ many servo-constructs for intimidation, security, and pursuit. The Rantal-class Venatus Reclamator is an advanced Cyber-Mastiff used by Exaction Squads. The R-VR\'s detectors enable the to track their prey, while their iron jaws can break bones or kill on command.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','EXACTION SQUAD, IMPERIUM, ADEPTUS ARBITES, ARBITES, R-VR CYBER-MASTIFF',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('IMP','AES','AES',9,'SUB','Arbites Subductor','Subductors possess one of the most recognisable - and feared - s