ably after the foe with a single-mindedness that is terrifying to behold. Others of the kind flock after them eager to join in the nightmare hunt.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','10','TOMB WORLD, NECRON, <DYNASTY>, FLAYED ONE, LEADER',0,'Combat,Scout'),('NEC','TW','FLO',0,'WAR','Flayed One Warrior','Tormented by a gruesome curse, Flayed Ones are warped in both mind and android body. Possessed of flensing finger-blades and a nightmarish hunger for flesh and blood, these awful creatures stalk their prey from the shadows and don their victims\' tattered hides after the kill.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','TOMB WORLD, NECRON, <DYNASTY>, FLAYED ONE, WARRIOR',0,'Combat,Scout'),('NEC','TW','IMM',0,'LDR','Immortal Leader','Some Immortals retain a little more of the sentience that was stolen from their kind during the horrors of biotransference. Far from benifitting the Immortal itself, these characteristics simply make them excellent squad leaders, ultimately furthering the whims of their overlords.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','3+','11','TOMB WORLD, NECRON, <DYNASTY>, IMMORTAL, LEADER',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('NEC','TW','IMM',0,'WAR','Immortal Warrior','Immortals are elite foot soldiers. They are built to endure even the most punishing firefights and close-quarters brawls. They also carry sizeable Gauss or Tesla firearms of their own, directing their formidable firepower with the ingrained tactical cunning that is their hallmark.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','3+','10','TOMB WORLD, NECRON, <DYNASTY>, IMMORTAL, WARRIOR',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('NEC','TW','NC',0,'NEC','Necron Warrior','The rank-and-file of the Necron legions are still formidable combatants. Android killers with just enough sentience to follow their masters\' commands, they are relentless and frighteningly resilient, and boast firepower sufficient to flay their victims down to the component atoms.','kt21','2[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','9','TOMB WORLD, NECRON, <DYNASTY>, NECRON WARRIOR',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','GSK','BOY',0,'BN','Boss Nob','Orks grow bigger and more belligerent the more they fight. Over time, the most experienced fighters become hulking greenskins. Nobz have survived endless war and infighting through a combination of strength, cunning, and the instinct to destroy anything that challenges them.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','13','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, LEADER, BOY, BOSS NOB',0,'Combat,Staunch'),('ORK','GSK','BOY',0,'FTR','Boy Fighter','Boys form the muscled, brutal majority of any teeming Ork horde. No self-respecting Ork would be without a loud slugga and at least one enormous choppa with which to vent their wild fury. They live only for the joy of violence and the clamouring din of war.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, BOY, FIGHTER',0,'Combat,Marksman'),('ORK','GSK','BOY',0,'GNR','Boy Gunner','Orks enjoy the din and recoil of the large firearms they refer to collectively as shootas, as much as the weapons\' gory results. Shootas are often cobbled together from scrap, but unleash hails of solid shot that can rip apart almost anything through sheer volume.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, BOY, GUNNER',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','GSK','BOY',0,'GRE','Gretchin','Gretchin - or grots - are stunted, sneaky, and vicious. They are more nimble than their Okr masters, able to squeeze through narrow spaces and operate more complicated gubbins. Their sharp eyes enable them to act as lookouts and sentries, and their screech of alarm is piercing.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','2','3','6+','5','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, BOY, GRETCHIN',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('ORK','GSK','CK',0,'FTR','Clan Kommando Fighter','Kommandos epitomise the Orky virtue of low cunning, taking a less directly confrontational approach to their peers. Few things make them happier than sneakin gup on an unsuspecting enemy and hacking, slashing, and shooting before the foe can strike back.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, CLAN KOMMANDO, FIGHTER',0,'Combat,Scout'),('ORK','GSK','CK',0,'NOB','Clan Kommando Nob','The sneakiest of all their tribe\'s sneaky gits, Kommando Nobs are both brutal and cunning enough to boss about the most conniving of their species as they lead espionage operations behind enemy lines.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','13','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, CLAN KOMMANDO, KOMMANDO NOB',0,'Combat,Staunch'),('ORK','GSK','SPE',0,'BUR','Burna Boy','Burna Boyz are pyromaniacs all, obsessed with raging infernos - the bigger and hotter the better. Their burnas can weed hiding enemies out of cover, belching roaring flames that rush into defensive networks and incinerate lighter barriers entirely.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, SPESHULIST, BURNA BOY',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','GSK','SPE',0,'LOO','Loota','Lootas are the most heavily armed of all Orks - because they steal the best weapons from everyone else! They are kleptomaniacs obsessed with owning and firing the loudest and most destructive guns, modifying them to make them ever more ostentatious and killy.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, SPESHULIST, LOOTA',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','GSK','SPE',0,'SPN','Spanner','On the lower hierarchical rungs of the madcap geniuses known as Meks, Spanners help to keep Ork technology working. They obsessively acquire loot and scrap to build weapons and contraptions, as well as kustom weapons that unleash strange energy beams or ammo.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','GREENSKIN, ORK, <CLAN>, LEADER, SPESHULIST, SPANNER',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',11,'BOM','Bomb Squig','Bomb squigs are among the most dangerous of their kind. In addition to being voracious predators, as the name suggests they carry all manner of explosives. In battle they race for the foe, blowing up enemy troops and destroying their defences.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','6+','6','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, BOMB SQUIG',0,'N/A'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',2,'BOY','Kommando Boy','Kommandos epitomise the Orky virtue of low cunning. Few things make them happier than sneaking up on an unsuspecting enemy and hacking, slashing and shooting before the foe strike back.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO BOY',0,'Scout,Staunch,Combat'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',5,'BRE','Kommando Breacha Boy','Kommando Breacha Boys have the task of barging into places and enemies \nalike and smashing them apart with their Breacha Rams. It is one they \nrelish, and those that see them in action and survive soon learn to \nespecially fear these brutal greenskins.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO BREACHA BOY',0,'Staunch,Combat'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',9,'BUR','Kommando Burna Boy','Burna Boyz are pyromaniacs all, obsessed with raging infernos - the \nbigger and hotter the better. Those of the Kommandos display an \nextraordinary patience, knowing the wait makes the devastation they \nwreak with their burnas even more satisfying.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO BURNA BOY',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',8,'COM','Kommando Comms Boy','There’s no excuse for not following the boss’ plan, no matter how \nquestionably sane it seems. Kommando Comms Boys perform the function of \nensuring no Ork ‘forgets’ their orders on the field by relaying the \nboss’ instructions.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO COMMS BOY',0,'Scout,Staunch'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',7,'DAK','Kommando Dakka Boy','The sound of roaring dakka is music to the ears of many Orks, not least to Kommando Dakka Boys. They take great delight in pouring vast quantities of bullets into the enemy, destroying light cover, sending foes running and causing pandemonium.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO DAKKA BOY',0,'Scout,Marksman'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',3,'GRT','Kommando Grot','For Grots to last long in the brutal reality of Ork society, they have to learn to lie, cheat, steal, sneak, suck up and plan - traits all valuable to Kommando kill teams.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','5','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO GROT',0,'Scout'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',1,'NOB','Kommando Nob','The sneakiest of sneaky gits, Kommando Nobs are both brutal and cunning \nenough to boss about the most conniving of their species.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','13','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO NOB, LEADER',0,'Staunch,Combat'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',10,'RKT','Kommando Rokkit Boy','Rising from hidden locations, Kommando Rokkit Boyz fire rockets at bunkers, fuel silos, ammo dumps or even into the midst of an unsuspecting enemy - all with a broad grin at the havoc they’ve caused.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO ROKKIT BOY',0,'Marksman'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',4,'SLA','Kommando Slasha Boy','Slasha Boyz love getting into the thick of action, even by Ork standards. Festooned with all manner of blades, they hack and slash their way through enemy after enemy.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO SLASHA BOY',0,'Scout,Staunch,Combat'),('ORK','KOM','KOM',6,'SNP','Kommando Snipa Boy','Though few Orks have the patience to be a Kommando Snipa Boy, those who perform the role are experts in finding the best spots to fire at the enemy, kill a target and enjoy watching the survivors flail and panic in the confusion inevitably caused.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, <CLAN>, KOMMANDO SNIPA BOY',0,'Marksman'),('ORK','KOM24','KOM24',2,'BOY','Kommando Boy','','kt24','6\"','2','0','0','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, BOY',0,''),('ORK','KOM24','KOM24',5,'BRC','Kommando Breacha Boy','','kt24','6\"','2','0','0','5+','10','KOMMANDO, ORK, BREACHA BOY',1,''),('ORK','KOM24','KOM24',9,'BRN','Kommando Burna Boy','','kt24','6\"','2','0','0','5+','10','KOMMANDO, OR