, T\'AU EMPIRE, KROOT, CARNIVORE, WARRIOR',0,'Combat,Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',1,'BH','Kroot Bow-Hunter','The accelerator bows wielded by these Kroot are distinctive weapons, with a Kroot rifle at their core. When fired, the bow\'s curves crackle with energy, charging the loaded arrow\'s head. Effects on struck enemies vary depending on the material the arrowhead is made from.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, BOW-HUNTER',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',2,'CB','Kroot Cold-Blood','Cold-Bloods have fought as mercenaries for many years indeed. They have seen and experienced much, and little inspires fear in them. The knowledge they have gained makes them adept with different ammunition types, selecting the optimum shot for each kill they wish to make.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','9','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, COLD-BLOOD',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',3,'CS','Kroot Cut-Skin','These Kroot have fully embraced close-combat fighting. Swift and ferocious, Cut-Skins launch a flurry of savage blows against their foes, giving the enemy no opportunity to strike back before they are cut down.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, CUT-SKIN',0,'Combat'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',4,'HGNR','Kroot Heavy Gunner','Kroot will fight for or against almost any race in the galaxy. In the process they are paid with - or steal - exotic weapons such as Dvorgite Skinners, which charge biological material to create a searing stream of energy, or Londaxi tribalests - anti-armour weapons that fire solid shots a high speeds.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, HEAVY GUNNER',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',5,'HND','Kroot Hound','Fast, nimble, ferocious, and incredibly loyal to their Kroot masters, Kroot hounds are natural companions to the Farstalker Kinbands. These beasts can steal into narrow passageways, recover objects, and rip foes apart with their beaked jaws.','kt21','4[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','7','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, HOUND',0,'Combat,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',0,'KB','Kroot Kill-Broker','Farstalker Kinbands are led by Kill-Brokers. These Kroot are not only expert tacticians and skilled fighters, but also able negotiators, ensuring their kin receive just rewards for their services.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','9','FARSTALKER KINBAND, LEADER, KROOT, KILL-BROKER',0,'Combat,Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',6,'LS','Kroot Long-Sight','The finest shots in Farstalker Kinbands, Long-Sights carry long-barrelled Kroot hunting rifles. They will gladly conceal themselves in position for days at a time to make the perfect shot. Few in their sights ever live to tell the tale.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, LONG-SIGHT',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',7,'PST','Kroot Pistolier','Cool under pressure and comfortable fighting close to the enemy, Kroot Pistoliers are dexterous and quick-thinking fighters. Once in optimum range, they unleash a fusillade from their pistols that is almost impossible to escape.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, PISTOLIER',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',8,'STK','Kroot Stalker','Even among Kroot, these warriors are particularly able infiltrators and hunters. They possess an almost preternatural understanding of terrain and the art of concealment, able to get extremely close to an enemy before moving in for the kill.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, STALKER',0,'Combat,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',9,'TRK','Kroot Tracker','These Kroot share a very strong personal bond with their Pech\'ra - a bird that hails from Pech itself. The two work in a synchronised manner to aid their kinband. The Pech\'ra can not only distract enemies, but also warn the Kroot of the foe\'s presense.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, TRACKER',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','FSKB','FSKB',10,'WAR','Kroot Warrior','Kroot Warriors are fierce fighters, expert hunters, and relentless trackers. Those of Farstalker Kindreds have spent many years as mercenaries, gaining much experience in was as well as consuming genetic material for the betterment of their kind\'s future.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','2','3','5+','8','FARSTALKER KINBAND, KROOT, WARRIOR',0,'Combat,Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'DS8','DS8 Tactical Support Turret','Tactical Support Turrets are automated defence batteries that provide support for Fire Warriors and T\'au kill teams. They are often deployed by Orca Dropships straight into fixed positions and add the considerable power of their missiles to the fight.','kt21','-','1','1','3','4+','9','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, DS8 TACTICAL SUPPORT TURRET',0,'Staunch,Marksman'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MB3','MB3 Recon Drone','These large drones are capable of collecting swathes of vital battlefield data that can make the difference between victory and defat. Being larger, they can also be mounted with heavier weaponry - their burst cannon can effectively suppress or cut down enemy infantry.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','12','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MB3 RECON DRONE',0,'Staunch,Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV1','MV1 Gun Drone','Using anti-gravitic motors and jet-thrusters, Gun Drones hover over the landscape, moving quickly to engage the enemy and record battlefield data. On kill team missions, they can distract enemies as well as partake in attacks alongside the T\'au warriors they serve.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV1  GUN DRONE',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV31','MV31 Pulse Accelerator Drone','Pulse Accelerator Drones boost the pulse weapons carried by Pathfinders, making the technology much more powerful and giving them a vital edge.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV31 PULSE ACCELERATOR DRONE',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV33','MV33 Grav-Inhibitor Drone','Grav-Inhibitor Drones are capable of manipulating gravity around, and significantly slowing the progress of, oncoming enemy troops. On countless occasions have Pathfinder kill teams escaped almost certain death thanks to the technology carried by these drones.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV33 GRAV-INHIBITOR DRONE',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV36','MV36 Guardian Drone','These defensive drones have emitters that project a protective energy field to nearby field amplifier units borne by other operatives. Those amplifiers pick up the shielding force field of the Guardian Drone and spread it in an energised umbrella over their bearer.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV36 GUARDIAN DRONE',0,'Staunch'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV4','MV4 Shield Drone','Shield Drones are fitted with shield generators rather than weaponry. It is their task to protect the Pathfinders they accompnay. Their saviour protocols ensure that, should a T\'au come under direct threat, the Shield Drone will protect them from harm.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV4 SHIELD DRONE',0,'Staunch'),('TAU','HC','DRN',0,'MV7','MV7 Marker Drone','The high-intensity markerlights used by Marker Drones are vital for the synergy of T\'au forces. They indicate priority targets both for the Pathfinders they are alongside as well as other powerful T\'au assets. Whatever they pick out will soon be obliterated.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, DRONE, FLY,  MV7 MARKER DRONE',0,'Staunch,Scout'),('TAU','HC','FW',0,'SL','Fire Warrior Shas\'La','Bred for war, Fire Warriors are rigorously trained soldiers committed wholly to the Greater Good. In addition to bearing powerful weapons systems and lightweight but durable body armour, their helmets contain sensors, target-tracking readouts, and communication uplinks.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, FIRE WARRIOR, SHAS\'LA',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','HC','FW',0,'SU','Fire Warrior Shas\'Ui','These veteran Fire Warriors are driven to ensure their team\'s cohesion and the following of textbook martial tenets. Able combat commanders, they quickly react to changing battlefield situations and easily adapt their plans in accordance with new orders.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','4+','8','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, LEADER, FIRE WARRIOR, SHAS\'UI',0,'Marksman'),('TAU','HC','PF',0,'HGNR','Pathfinder Heavy Gunner','Some Pathfinders wield their killteam\'s heavy weapons. Their task is a relitevely simple one - to kill or destroy what their Shas\'ui orders them to or what they deem to be an important target.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, PATHFINDER, HEAVY GUNNER',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','HC','PF',0,'SL','Pathfinder Shas\'La','Even the rank-and-file of Pathfinder teams are selfless adherents to the Greater Good, eagerly volunteering themselves for the most dangerous missions. They operate close to the enemy to learn all they can from them, as well as engaging them when necessary.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','7','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, PATHFINDER, SHAS\'LA',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','HC','PF',0,'SU','Pathfinder Shas\'Ui','Shas\'ui Pathfinders are veteran warriors who have fought in many campaigns. They have passed dangerous trials of fire to reach the rank, and are dynamic and accomplished tacticians more than capable of leading their team to victory.','kt21','3[CIRCLE]','2','1','3','5+','8','HUNTER CADRE, T\'AU, <SEPT>, LEADER, PATHFINDER, HEAVY GUNNER',0,'Marksman,Scout'),('TAU','HC','SBS',0,'SU','Stealth Battlesuit Shas\'Ui','Expert in fighting as \'lone wolves\', warriors in Stealth Battlesuits go behind enemy lines, seeking to destroy important targets. Their 