hysical and climbable part of a terrain feature in order to climb it.</li>\n <li>Each time this operative drops, the intended location can be any vertical distance from the level it occupies.</li>\n <li>Each time this operative drops, it counts any vertical distance it travels as half for that drop.</li>\n </ul>','Ability','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','FBS',6,'1','Firestorm Bolt Shells','Select a Bolt Shotgun the operative (excluding THEYN) is equipped with. That weapon gains the following additional profile for the battle.\n <table class=\"eqtable\" width=\"100%\">\n    <tr>\n		<th>Name</th>\n		<th>A</th>\n		<th>BS</th>\n		<th>D</th>\n	</tr>\n	<tr>\n		<td>Firestorm Bolt Shells</td>\n		<td>4</td>\n		<td>3+</td>\n		<td>2/4</td>\n	</tr>\n	<tr>\n		<th colspan=\"4\">Special Rules</th>\n    </tr>\n	<tr>\n		<td colspan=\"4\">Rng [PENT], Blast [TRI]</td>\n    </tr>\n</table>','Weapon','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','HKY','THEYN','FBS-THEYN',6,'1','Firestorm Bolt Shells (THEYN)','Select a Bolt Shotgun the operative is equipped with. That weapon gains the following additional profile for the battle.\r  <table class=\"eqtable\" width=\"100%\">\r     <tr>\r 		<th>Name</th>\r 		<th>A</th>\r 		<th>BS</th>\r 		<th>D</th>\r 	</tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<td>Firestorm Bolt Shells</td>\r 		<td>4</td>\r 		<td>2+</td>\r 		<td>2/4</td>\r 	</tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<th colspan=\"4\">Special Rules</th>\r     </tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<td colspan=\"4\">Rng [PENT], Blast [TRI]</td>\r     </tr>\r </table>','Weapon','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','GCG',7,'2','Gravitic Concussion Grenade','The operative is equipped with the following ranged weapon for the battle:\r  <table class=\"eqtable\" width=\"100%\">\r     <tr>\r 		<th>Name</th>\r 		<th>A</th>\r 		<th>BS</th>\r 		<th>D</th>\r 	</tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<td>Gravitic Concussion Grenade</td>\r 		<td>4</td>\r 		<td>3+</td>\r 		<td>2/4</td>\r 	</tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<th colspan=\"4\">Special Rules</th>\r     </tr>\r 	<tr>\r 		<td colspan=\"4\">Rng [PENT], Blast [CIRCLE], Indirect, Limited</td>\r     </tr>\r </table>','Weapon','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','KVCU',8,'1','KV-Ceramide Undersuit','The operative gains the following ability for the battle:<br/>\n<strong>KV-Ceramide Undersuit:</strong>\nEach time a shooting attack is made against this operative, if the ranged weapon has the Blast or Torrent special rule, in the Roll Defence Dice step of that shooting attack, you can re-roll one of your Defence Dice.\nThis operative is unaffected by the Splash critical hit rule.','Ability','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','PK',1,'2','Plasma Knife','The operative is equipped with the following melee weapon for the battle:\n <table class=\"eqtable\" width=\"100%\">\n 	<tr>\n 		<th>Name</th>\n 	   <th>A</th>\n 	   <th>BS</th>\n 	   <th>D</th>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n 		<td>Plasma Knife</td>\n 	   <td>4</td>\n 	   <td>4+</td>\n 	   <td>3/5</td>\n     </tr>\n     <tr>\n 		<th colspan=\"4\">Special Rules</th>\n 	</tr>\n 	<tr>\n 		<td colspan=\"4\">Lethal 5+</td>\n 	</tr>\n </table>','Weapon','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-CS',403,'2','Concussion Shells','The operative gains the following ability for the battle:<br/>\n<strong>Concussion Shells:</strong>\nSelect a Bolt Revolver or the Short Range profile of a Bolt Shotgun the operative is equipped with. That weapon or weapon profile gains the Stun critical hit rule for the battle.','Ability','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-DEG',405,'2/3','Delver\'s Eyeglass','If the operative is a RIFLEKYN or GUNNER, this Rare Equipment costs 3EP. Otherwise, it costs 2EP.<br/>\nThe operative gains the following ability for the battle:<br/>\n<strong>Delver\'s Eyeglass:</strong>\nWhen determining Line of Sight for this operative, enemy operatives are not Obscured.','Ability','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-DSW',401,'2','Darkstar Weapon','Select a throwing Plasma Knife or one of the operative\'s melee weapons. That weapon gains the Rending critical hit rule for the battle.','WepMod','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-RVS',406,'1','Relic Voidsuit','The operative gains the following ability for the battle:<br/>\n<strong>Relic Voidsuit:</strong>\nEach time a shooting attack is made against this operative, in the Roll Defence Dice step of that shooting attack, you can retain one of your successful normal saves as a critical save instead.','Ability','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-SI',402,'3','Spectral Implant','In the Ready Operatives step of each Turning Point, if this operative is in the killzone and more than [PENT] from enemy operatives, add one Resourceful Point to your pool.','Ability','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','RE-WFG',404,'2','Weavefield Gorget','The operative gains the following ability for the battle:<br/>\n<strong>Weavefield Gorget:</strong>\nThis operative has a 4+ Invulnerable Save for the battle.','Ability','','','','','Rare Equipment'),('VOT','HKY','','','SS',5,'1','Stabilised Shells','Operative equipped with a Bolt Shotgun only. In the Set Up Operatives step, select a type of ammnunition for this operative to have loaded into its Bolt Shotgun for the battle: Standard Shells or Stabilised Shells.\nIf it has loaded Standard Shells, it uses either profile of its Bolt Shotgun as normal. If it has loaded Stabilised Shells, it can only use the Long Range profile of its Bolt Shotgun, but att 1 to both Damage characteristics of that profile and improve its Ballistic Skill characteristics by 1 for that operative.\n<br/>\nThe operative can perform the following action during the battle:<br/>\n<strong>Load Shotgun (1 AP):</strong><br/>\nChange the type of ammunition loaded into the Bolt Shotgun this operative is equipped with.','Action','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY24','','','FSBS',1,'0','Firestorm Bolt Shells','Once per turning point, when a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operative is performing the Shoot action and you select a bolt shotgun (short range), you can use this rule.\nIf you do, until the end of that action, that weapon has the Blast 1\" weapon rule.','Ability','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY24','','','KVCU',2,'0','KV-Ceramide Undersuit','Whenever an enemy operative is shooting a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operative, if the ranged weapon in that sequence has the Blast or Torrent weapon rule, you can re-roll one of your defence dice.\nIn addition, friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operatives are not affected by the X\" Devastating X weapon rule (i.e, Devastating with a distance) unless they are the target during that sequence.','Ability','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY24','','','PK',3,'0','Plasma Knives','Friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operatives have the following melee weapon. Note that some operatives already have this weapon but with better stats; in that instance use the better version.\n<table class=\"eqtable\">\n<tr>\n<th>Name</th><th>ATK</th><th>HIT</th><th>DMG</th><th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Plasma Knife</td><td>3</td><td>4+</td><td>3/5</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"4\">Weapon Rules</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Lethal 5+</td>\n</tr>\n</table>','Weapon','','','','','Equipment'),('VOT','HKY24','','','SBS',4,'0','Stabilized Bolt Shells','Up to twice per turning point, whenever a friendly HERNKYN YAEGIR operative is performing the Shoot action and you selected a bolt shotgun (long range), you can use this rule.\nIf you do, until the end of that action, improve the Hit stat of that weapon by 1 and add 1 to both of its damage stats.','Ability','','','','','Equipment');
